Package: hlabud
Title: Tidy Methods for Analysis of the Human Leukocyte Antigen (HLA) Genes from IMGTHLA
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kamil", "Slowikowski", , "kslowikowski@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2843-6370"))
Description: Methods for analysis of HLA genes at the amino acid level, using data from IMGTHLA. The functions return simple lists and matrices ready for downstream analysis with packages like `lme4` and `uwot`.
